HAI 1.4
    HOW IZ I divmod YR a AN YR b
        I HAS A result ITZ A BUKKIT
        result HAS A quotient ITZ QUOSHUNT OF a AN b
        result HAS A remainder ITZ MOD OF a AN b
        FOUND YR result
    IF U SAY SO

    I HAS A r ITZ I IZ divmod YR 17 AN YR 5 MKAY
    VISIBLE "17 / 5 = " AN r'Z quotient AN " REMAINDER " AN r'Z remainder
KTHXBYE
